text: Chaumont Volley-Ball 52 is a professional volleyball team based in Chaumont, in France. And have played in Ligue A since the 2012-2013 season. It won the 2017 French League and the French Supercup in 2017 and 2021. The club finished second in the same year of the CEV Cup.
